{{Documentation subpage}}
<kbd>Country_data</kbd> templates are also available for the [[Kingdom of the Netherlands]] (of which Sint Maarten is a country) and [[Netherlands Antilles]] (of which Sint Maarten was part):
{| style="background-color:#ecfcf4"
|-
| [[Template:Country data Netherlands Antilles]] || {{flag|Netherlands Antilles}}
|-
| [[Template:Country data Kingdom of the Netherlands]] || {{flag|Kingdom of the Netherlands}}
|}
templates are also available for the  French part of the island:
{| style="background-color:#ecfcf4"
|-
| [[Template:Country data Saint Martin]] || {{flag|Saint Martin}}
|-
|}<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
